<HEADLINE> Mkapa Holds Talks With DPRK FM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, March 29 (Xinhua) -- Tanzanian President
Benjamin Mkapa held talks with visiting Democratic People's
Republic of Korea (DPRK) Deputy Prime Minister and Minister for
Foreign Affairs, Kim Yong Nam, here today.
</P>
