Philippine city of Cebu next week to discuss measures to
accelerate the development of financial and capital markets in the
region.
</P>
<P>
Some 200 delegates, led by the finance ministers of the APEC
member economies, are expected to attend the April 4-6 meeting,
the Philippine government said today.
</P>
<P>
