<HEADLINE> Ukraine Edges Albania 1-0 in World Cup Qualifier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, March 29 (Xinhua) -- Ukraine took a narrow 1-0 win over
Albania in World Cup qualifying group nine in Granada, Spain, on
Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Ukraine went ahead just before half-time when Andriy Shevchenko
advanced down the right before finding Serguei Rebrov, who had no
problem beating goalkeeper Foto Strakosha.
</P>
<P>
