Albanian goalkeeper Foto Strakosha turned in a superb
performance but in the end Albania were left looking for their
first win in the group after three defeats and a draw.
</P>
<P>
The game was moved to Spain because of civil unrest in the
Balkan country and had only 250 spectators. 
