unmarked three meters from goal but shot wide.
</P>
<P>
Russia tops the standings with eight points from four games but
could be overhauled on Sunday when Israel, currently on seven
points, visit Luxembourg. Bulgaria are third on six points and
play Cyprus on April 2.
</P>
