<HEADLINE> Muslims, Croats Fail on Joint Police Force in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SARAJEVO, March 29 (Xinhua) -- Bosnian Muslims and Croats
failed today to agree on establishing a joint police in the
central town zone of Mostar.
</P>
<P>
