<HEADLINE> Qiao Shi Visits Modern Cinema Center in France </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
POITIERS, France, March 29 (Xinhua) -- Qiao Shi, chairman of
the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress of China,
today visited the modern cinema center of Futuroscope near
Poitiers, the department of Vienne, under the company of French
Senate President Rene Monory.
</P>
<P>
Qiao Shi and his wife Yu Wen watched movies of hemispheric
images in three dimensions in the cinemas of the Futuroscope and
had a dinner together with Monory and Madame Monory.
